data.description: Gorgeous well maintained four bedroom two bath home with carpet and tile throughout the home. This home features an open spacious living area with a wood burning fireplace and a eat-in breakfast bar overlooking the living area and backyard area. The kitchen has stainless steel appliances with ceramic tile and stone countertops giving it lots of character. All rooms are spacious with a guest bathroom and office that can also be used as a room and the primary bedroom with a large bathroom and closet. Refrigerator stays with a acceptable offer.
